  m_text: "Note: \nThis tool is in initial development as a side project for me to
    learn HDR in Unity and experiment with displays. \n\nThe focus of this tool is
    to be \"Effectively correct\" for gamers and creators to easily digest and learn
    from. Meaning I may not use correct terminology or get into too much details.
    Just explain things as I feel is easiest to understand.\n\nIn the future I'll
    add information from my findings, more tests, more examples and information. "
